{"tid":209076,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"專業旅運主任索回佣還柙","createTime":"2017-04-20T02:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T03:45:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd9fd87429c11960df74ddd12d912d7410bd3410","tid":209076,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T02:36:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19995568&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19995568%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170420&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8FKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=7d45341b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19995568%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170420&h=5bfb3560\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19995568&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170420</a><br />\n<br />\n專業旅運主任索回佣還柙<br />\n<br />\n法庭&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n專業旅運一名櫃枱主任向女下屬索取5,100元回佣，還柙至下月2日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】專業旅運一名前櫃枱主任獲晉升後，須將自己以往的顧客定單轉交其他營業代表，他轉交女下屬後，令對方可獲約6,100元佣金，但多次要求她提供5,100元回佣，最終被廉署拘控。他昨承認索賄罪，還柙至下月2日判刑。<br />\n辯方為被告陳賢傑（34歲）求情時指陳工作勤力，妻子需接受精神治療，陳另需照顧父親及祖母，雖明知會判即時監禁，望能視作例外情況而輕判。<br />\n案情指，陳於2010年加入專業旅運當旅遊顧問，需向顧客銷售旅行產品，去年2月晉升為主任，須將顧客轉介給其他營業代表。他於去年3月將兩張定單轉交女下屬，並於3月至5月間多次向她索取回佣，女下屬通知管理層。<br />\n案件編號：ESCC908/17<br />\n■記者戴國輝"},{"pid":"d3f1324dc05a081410e944dbf1252b50fb291e75","tid":209076,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T02:39:09.000Z","msg":"6100佣，想抽人5100<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa7da8f187eb469f5d01aabced7c8023c579d8d","tid":209076,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017